text: Stefan Armbruster (born 26 March 1953) is a German coxswain who represented West Germany. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics in Mexico City with the men's coxed four where they came twelfth. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Baden-Baden Category:Coxswains (rowing)
